schemas close
* Exercise both SETORDER forms for each tag: with TAG keyword and bare form
COLOR DEFAULT
USE students noindex
SETCNX students.cnx
* LNAME
SETORDER students.cnx TAG LNAME --asc
STATUS
LIST
SETORDER students.cnx LNAME --desc
STATUS
LIST
* SID
SETORDER students.cnx TAG SID --asc
STATUS
LIST
SETORDER students.cnx SID --desc
STATUS
LIST
* GPA
SETORDER students.cnx TAG GPA --asc
STATUS
LIST
SETORDER students.cnx GPA --desc
STATUS
LIST
* MAJOR
SETORDER students.cnx TAG MAJOR --asc
STATUS
LIST
SETORDER students.cnx MAJOR --desc
STATUS
LIST
* end
